item.title: starshopping by lil peep
item.description: Wait right here I’ll be back in the mornin’ I know that I’m not that important to you But to me, girl, you’re so much more than gorgeous So much more than perfect (yeah) Right now I know that I’m not really worth it If you give me time, I can work on it Give me some time while I work on it Losin’ your patience, and, girl, I don’t blame you
